title: Citizen Eco-Drive Silhouette Crystal Womens Watch FE1154-57A - Overview
description:
Citizen Eco-Drive Silhouette Crystal Womens Watch - FE1154-57A http://www.abt.com/product/92560/Citizen-FE115457A.html

Freshen up your watch collection this season ladies with the new Citizen Silhouette Crystal. Fashion forward and ready to be shown off with a unique decorated dial with Swarovski crystals. Shown here in a two-tone stainless steel case and bracelet with silver dial featuring date.
Specifications:
• Movement: Eco-Drive J710
• Functions: 3-Hand with Date
• Band: Two-Tone Stainless Steel Bracelet Fold Over Clasp with Push Button
• Case Material: Two-Tone Stainless Steel Swarovski Crystal Bezel
• Crystal Mineral: Sapphire Crystal
• Water-Resistance: 30M
